{"tid":48470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極光飄雪嘉年華 摩士公園變身北歐小鎮","createTime":"2016-12-21T05:52:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T06:15:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"343dcccc2132876a4be2f687429aa2f5f56dfcb1","tid":48470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:52:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161221/19872630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161221%2F19872630&d=E0Za%2BMemw7y9CMrK2FtVZEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=cd9de475\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161221%2F19872630&h=9038a44c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161221/19872630</a><br />\n<br />\n極光飄雪嘉年華<br />\n摩士公園變身北歐小鎮<br />\n<br />\n19,547<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n東華三院今年聖誕節將黃大仙摩士公園游泳池變身北歐小鎮，舉辦「極光飄雪嘉年華」，即日起至明年1月14日開放，嘉年華場地設置了歐陸式小屋及聖誕許願樹、鐘樓、旋轉木馬等節日裝飾，更引入全港首個最大型戶外虛擬星空及北極光裝置，每晚6時起的正點時間上演「極光飄雪匯演」，有燈光、音響和飄雪效果。<br />\n<br />\n嘉年華又設有多個手工藝攤位，包括押花、禪繞畫、皮革製作、扭波波、印度彩繪Henna等工作坊，戲水池位置擺放了一隻1.7米高的巨型黃鴨及數千隻黃色小鴨，市民可拍照留念。場內大部分手工藝、遊樂活動及食物攤位，由東華三院旗下社企及屬下單位主理。市民可免費參加遊戲攤位及手工藝攤位，美食攤檔另行收費，款項全數撥捐支持東華三院的社會服務。<br />\n<br />\n日期：即日至2017年1月14日<br />\n地點：黃大仙摩士公眾泳池空地<br />\n（免費入場）  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n【動畫】又係觀塘警區　總督察疑傳下體照畀女下屬<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n與妻慶生後約友消遣　心臟病漢淺酌暴斃"},{"pid":"a0063b81db3be7649020f7e87ad657e34f90f253","tid":48470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/video/20161221/org/1482263567_085d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fvideo%2F20161221%2Forg%2F1482263567_085d.jpg&h=336c1a6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c74f0ef92c7031bc35f184a7b4bb6f1f28e3434","tid":48470,"uid":65371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"下一則<br />\n與妻慶生後約友消遣　心臟病漢淺酌暴斃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c24ea2bd669700c19fdf5c26c9eb5186a456f5c","tid":48470,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:04:41.000Z","msg":"邊撚到北邊撚到歐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f83833a758c0ec0483a09d961d88c4312041491","tid":48470,"uid":28074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:09:06.000Z","msg":"北歐佈景版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15961cc4da401a21f96aeac7f78961d680b942e4","tid":48470,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9158097590069b539032437b3ba6f3b9afd1f9e8","tid":48470,"uid":22422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:12:45.000Z","msg":"免費嘅係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda62235e0352de3faf917934afb20712ebb0188","tid":48470,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無迷你龍你請我都唔去</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}